Skirmish: At sites 1[T] to 4[T], add a burden and discard this possession to cancel a skirmish involving Frodo. At any other site, discard this possession to remove a burden and heal Frodo. <br>
Neither weather nor searching eyes found Frodo. <br>
4 R 303 <br>
<br>
Knocked on the Head (0) <br>
Event <br>
Regroup: Play an unbound Hobbit from your discard pile. <br>
&quot;&#39;I wonder if poor Merry is much hurt.&#39;&quot; <br>
4 C 308 <br>
<br>
Light Shining Faintly (0) <br>
Event <br>
Fellowship: Add a burden to heal a Ring-bound companion twice. <br>
&quot;&#39;He&#39;s like that, and sometimes it shines through, somehow.&#39;&quot; <br>
4 U 309 <br>
<br>
•Merry, Unquenchable Hobbit (1) <br>
Companion - Hobbit <br>
3/4/G <br>
Skirmish: If Merry is not assigned to a skirmish, discard him to remove a (Sauron) Orc from a skirmish involving an unbound companion. <br>
&quot;&#39;All Wizards should have a hobbit or two in their care - to teach them the meaning of the word, and to correct them.&#39;&quot; <br>
